components.name: Check and Download Ensembl Files
components.description: Checks for new versions of Ensembl genomic mapping files and downloads updated versions to the S3 raw landing zone. Uses AirflowSkipException if no new versions are found.
outputs: Updated genomic mapping files in S3 raw landing zone

components.name: Process Ensembl Files with Spark
components.description: Processes the downloaded Ensembl mapping files using Spark to create structured tables in the data lake.
outputs: Processed Ensembl mapping tables in the data lake
